  "detailed_description": "Blockchain Tycoon is the cryptocurrency simulation game where you build and manage your own mining operation. Create your own coin, mine it, invest in other coins, upgrade and overclock GPUs or you can just HODL.<br><br>Mine coins in Campaign, Scenario, Challenge, and Sandbox Modes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>REALISTIC CRYPTOCURRENCY MINING SIMULATION</strong></h2><br>Simulate a mining operation. Play with realistic reward calculations, halving values based on real world algorithms such as SHA256 or algorithms created and optimized specifically for this game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824450/extras/37788b435b371f5c9d1795a50564994e.poster.avif?t=1710350703\" width=672 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824450/extras/37788b435b371f5c9d1795a50564994e.webm?t=1710350703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824450/extras/37788b435b371f5c9d1795a50564994e.mp4?t=1710350703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MINE WITH ASIC AND GPU</strong></h2><br>Variable hashrates for mining hardware depending on the algorithm, so you can build the right setup for maximum profit. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824450/extras/52b159b58e7679b3b1cb5c67ee1f9b1e.poster.avif?t=1710350703\" width=672 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824450/extras/52b159b58e7679b3b1cb5c67ee1f9b1e.webm?t=1710350703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824450/extras/52b159b58e7679b3b1cb5c67ee1f9b1e.mp4?t=1710350703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PUSH IT TO THE LIMIT</strong></h2><br>Overclock your hardware for the maximum power.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824450/extras/330f205abc3a6ec92cc478978d702c4f.poster.avif?t=1710350703\" width=672 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824450/extras/330f205abc3a6ec92cc478978d702c4f.webm?t=1710350703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824450/extras/330f205abc3a6ec92cc478978d702c4f.mp4?t=1710350703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TOKENS, EXCHANGE, INVESTING, STAKING</strong></h2><br>Take part in all aspects of the crypto game. Buy and sell tokens. Stake tokens for profit. Invest in other ICOs and try your luck. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824450/extras/fd867a6d34829a890d1108848eb34e41.poster.avif?t=1710350703\" width=672 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824450/extras/fd867a6d34829a890d1108848eb34e41.webm?t=1710350703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824450/extras/fd867a6d34829a890d1108848eb34e41.mp4?t=1710350703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>INITIAL COIN OFFERING</strong></h2><br>Gather your team and create your own currency. Manage your project and raise funds in your ICO. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824450/extras/a7cb6016e9d2333ac7e5087664ede9ce.poster.avif?t=1710350703\" width=672 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824450/extras/a7cb6016e9d2333ac7e5087664ede9ce.webm?t=1710350703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824450/extras/a7cb6016e9d2333ac7e5087664ede9ce.mp4?t=1710350703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GO GREEN</strong></h2><br>Produce your own power using solar panels and wind turbines. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824450/extras/ddd67cdd213733f4227ae401e596f26d.poster.avif?t=1710350703\" width=672 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824450/extras/ddd67cdd213733f4227ae401e596f26d.webm?t=1710350703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824450/extras/ddd67cdd213733f4227ae401e596f26d.mp4?t=1710350703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
